	(text_box "E = 1/2*C*V^2\nSome testing shows that the energy needed to blow a cap with 5.1A output current is ~65 joules. Output capacitance needed assuming only a 10V drop in output voltage is 1.3 Farads\nTesting also shows that 2A of current is not enough to blow the cap, it instead just fizzles"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
